CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 26, 2007

[Cite as 06/26/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-3189.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-1697. Chillicothe Tel. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 05-1298-TP-UNC. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. On October 10, 2006, this court stayed proceedings in this case pending the conclusion of related proceedings.

It is ordered by the court, sua sponte, that appellant shall file a notice advising this court of the status of the related proceedings within 15 days of the date of this entry.
